<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">
  <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="4; url=/">
  <title>404 - Page Not Found | U-TV REVIEW</title>
  <style>
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{
      margin:0;
      min-height:100vh;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      background:radial-gradient(circle at top,#12131a 0%,#050508 100%);
      color:#fff;
      font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;
      padding:20px;
    }
    .box{
      width:100%;
      max-width:560px;
      background:#0f111a;
      border:1px solid #1e2235;
      border-radius:24px;
      padding:30px 24px;
      text-align:center;
      box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
    }
    h1{
      margin:0 0 12px;
      font-size:2rem;
      line-height:1.2;
    }
    p{
      margin:0 0 20px;
      color:#cbd5e1;
      line-height:1.7;
    }
    a{
      display:inline-block;
      background:#ea4c23;
      color:#fff;
      text-decoration:none;
      padding:11px 18px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-weight:700;
    }
    .note{
      margin-top:14px;
      font-size:.85rem;
      color:#94a3b8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box">
    <h1>404 - Page Not Found</h1>
    <p>Jo page aap dhoondh rahe hain wo available nahi hai. Aapko home page par bheja ja raha hai.</p>
    <a href="/">Go Home</a>
    <div class="note">Redirecting in 4 seconds...</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
